_sText:
This map is my first release, it's a city type map made for Gun Game or RPG mods only. No buyzones or objectives. This a small map (20 max) but has plenty of places to move around including a tunnel, a tower, buidlings, roof tops, and more. I have yet to test on a full server and am awaiting feedback. Please let me know about any problems that i will address for the final release. 

MillaTime
